<h3 id="清单">清单</h3>
<ul>
  <li>物品清单
    <ul>
      <li>Mac(PC也可)</li>
      <li>Pico开发板（有排针, ¥35）</li>
      <li>MicroUSB（要可传数据）</li>
      <li>面包线若干</li>
      <li>1286 oled屏(¥30)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>软件清单
    <ul>
      <li>Pico驱动<a href="https://micropython.org/download/rp2-pico/"></a></li>
      <li>Pico开发工具<a href="https://thonny.org/">Thonny</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4 id="配置raspberry-pico">配置Raspberry Pico</h4>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.raspberrypi.com/documentation/microcontrollers/micropython.html">官方教程</a>
    <ol>
      <li>软件准备
        <ul>
          <li>下载并安装Thonny</li>
          <li>下载 MicroPython UF2 文件</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>硬件连接准备：
        <ul>
          <li>连好硬件</li>
          <li>点击Pico开关</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>找到可被系统识别的存储器：RPI-RP2
        <ul>
          <li>将 MicroPython UF2 文件拷贝到 RPI-RP2内</li>
          <li>RPI-RP2 会消失不见</li>
          <li>通过 Thonny 连接 Pico
            <ul>
              <li>工具 -&gt; 设置 -&gt; 解释器
  <img src="/images/2021-10-30-thonny_setting.png" alt="/images/2021-10-30-thonny_setting.png" /></li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </li>
</ul>
